[illuminate 组件](https://github.com/illuminate)都是独立 composer 包，`illuminate/validation` 在非 Laravel 项目里也能跑——手动把 `FileLoader → Translator → Factory` 三件套接起来即可。

## 安装

```bash
composer require illuminate/validation illuminate/translation illuminate/filesystem
```

> `illuminate/filesystem` 不是 `illuminate/validation` 的依赖，用 `FileLoader` 必须单独装。

## 准备语言文件

从 [Laravel-Lang/lang](https://github.com/Laravel-Lang/lang) 复制要用的语言文件到本地，例如 `lang/zh-CN/validation.php`。

## 装配

```php
use Illuminate\Filesystem\Filesystem;
use Illuminate\Translation\FileLoader;
use Illuminate\Translation\Translator;
use Illuminate\Validation\Factory;

$loader = new FileLoader(new Filesystem(), __DIR__ . '/../lang');
$translator = new Translator($loader, 'zh-CN');
$validator = new Factory($translator);
```

## 用

```php
$v = $validator->make(
    ['name' => ''],
    ['name' => 'required|string|min:2'],
);

if ($v->fails()) {
    print_r($v->errors()->all());
}
```

完整规则参考 Laravel 文档的 [Manually Creating Validators](https://laravel.com/docs/validation#manually-creating-validators)。

`strpos($haystack, $needle): int|false` 找不到时返回 `false`，**找到时返回位置 int**——位置 `0` 在 `if` 里跟 `false` 等价，会被吞掉。

```php
$s = 'abc';

if (strpos($s, 'a')) {            // 不输出，0 被当 false
    echo 'found';
}

if (strpos($s, 'a') !== false) {  // 正解
    echo 'found';
}
```

PHP 8.0+ 直接用 `str_contains($haystack, $needle): bool`，没有这个坑。

<https://www.php.net/manual/zh/function.strpos.php>

The newest note shows up here in full — a 60ch slot above the masonry grid. Everything else is a preview card.

Astro returns collection entries in **disk order**, not date order. Sort first, then split:

```ts
const notes = (await getCollection('notes')).sort(
  (a, b) => b.data.date.valueOf() - a.data.date.valueOf(),
);
const [hero, ...rest] = notes;
```

That's the whole trick.
